        <h2>Advisory Services</h2>
        <p>Investment advisory services are offered through Capital Wealth. Michael Stevens is an Investment Adviser Representative (IAR) and adheres to the fiduciary standard of care.</p>
        <p>Capital Wealth is a registered investment adviser. Registration does not imply any level of skill or training. The presence of this website shall not be directly or indirectly interpreted as a solicitation of investment advisory services to persons of another jurisdiction unless otherwise permitted by statute.</p>

        <h2>Fiduciary Standard</h2>
        <p>As fiduciary advisors, we are legally obligated to act in our clients' best interests at all times. This means we provide objective advice free from conflicts of interest. We do not receive commissions from the sale of financial products.</p>

        <h2>Investment Risks</h2>
        <p>Investing involves risk, including the potential loss of principal. Past performance is not indicative of future results. No investment strategy can guarantee a profit or protect against loss in periods of declining values.</p>
        <p>Diversification and asset allocation do not ensure a profit or protect against a loss. There is no guarantee that any particular asset allocation or mix of funds will meet your investment objectives or provide you with a given level of income.</p>

        <h2>Tax & Legal Information</h2>
        <p>Capital Wealth does not provide tax or legal advice. The tax-related information presented on this website is for general informational purposes only. Clients should consult with their qualified tax and legal professionals regarding their specific situation.</p>
        <p>Any tax-related information or strategies discussed are based on current tax laws, which are subject to change at any time.</p>

        <h2>Case Studies & Hypothetical Examples</h2>
